me":"Computation.destruct_eq_pure","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L104-L112"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">unsafe def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.run\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">run</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`run c` is an unsound meta function that runs `c` to completion, possibly\nresulting in an infinite loop in the VM. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.run","kind":"def","line":96,"name":"Computation.run","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L96-L102"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.destruct\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">destruct</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum\">⊕</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`destruct c` is the destructor for `Computation α` as a coinductive type.\nIt returns `inl a` if `c = pure a` and `inr c'` if `c = think c'`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.destruct","kind":"def","line":89,"name":"Computation.destruct","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L89-L94"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.runFor\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">runFor</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`runFor c n` evaluates `c` for `n` steps and returns the result, or `none`\nif it did not terminate after `n` steps. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.runFor","kind":"def","line":84,"name":"Computation.runFor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L84-L87"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.instInhabited\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabited</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.instInhabited","kind":"instance","line":81,"name":"Computation.instInhabited","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L81-L82"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.empty\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">empty</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`empty α` is the computation that never returns, an infinite sequence of\n`think`s. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.empty","kind":"def","line":76,"name":"Computation.empty","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L76-L79"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.tail\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">tail</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`tail c` is the remainder of computation, either `c` if `c = pure a`\nor `c'` if `c = think c'`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.tail","kind":"def","line":71,"name":"Computation.tail","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L71-L74"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.head\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">head</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`head c` is the first step of computation, either `some a` if `c = pure a`\nor `none` if `c = think c'`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.head","kind":"def","line":65,"name":"Computation.head","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L65-L68"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.thinkN\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">thinkN</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`thinkN c n` is the computation that delays for `n` ticks and then performs\ncomputation `c`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.thinkN","kind":"def","line":58,"name":"Computation.thinkN","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L58-L62"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.think\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">think</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`think c` is the computation that delays for one \"tick\" and then performs\ncomputation `c`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.think","kind":"def","line":50,"name":"Computation.think","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L50-L56"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.instCoeTC\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">instCoeTC</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Coe.html#CoeTC\">CoeTC</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.instCoeTC","kind":"instance","line":46,"name":"Computation.in